## Description {#details}

This file defines a special form of Alias Analysis called <code>Provenance / Analysis&#39;&#39;. </code>

The word provenance&#39;&#39; refers to the history of the ownership / of an object. Thus &#96;â€˜Provenance Analysis`&#39; is an analysis which attempts to use various techniques to determine if locally

WARNING: This file knows about how certain Objective-C library functions are used. Naive LLVM IR transformations which would otherwise be behavior-preserving may break these assumptions.
